{
  "title": "CentOS7 安装 VirtualBox 辅助工具包",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div class=\"article fmt article__content\" data-id=\"1190000006233585\" data-license=\"sa\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.6; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em;\"></p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">如果你想主机和虚拟机之间能自由切换，共享剪切板，共享文件和文件夹，那就安装这个包吧。</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">不知道为什么，我通过 virtualbox 的 devices 菜单的 insert Guest Additions CD image… 选项就是无法完成装载。</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\"><img id=\"<0B8C1E02-3348-443A-B903-C8A962419164>\" src=\"quiver-image-url/A8C8F3AA1495BB7677BDD3BD64195553.png\" alt=\"bVAaKV\" data-src=\"/img/bVAaKV\" apple-inline=\"yes\" apple-width=\"yes\" apple-height=\"yes\" class=\"Apple-web-attachment Singleton\" subtitle=\"正在下载…\" progress=\"0.01\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); vertical-align: middle; padding: 3px; cursor: pointer; display: inline; position: static !important;\" width=\"297\" height=\"218\"></p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">错误如下：</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\"><img id=\"<EA95DB30-A97E-43FE-8759-3EDD3F5A492A>\" src=\"quiver-image-url/A9B485D5499F4A75F0B034F0C351514C.png\" alt=\"bVAaLm\" data-src=\"/img/bVAaLm\" apple-inline=\"yes\" apple-width=\"yes\" apple-height=\"yes\" class=\"Apple-web-attachment Singleton\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); vertical-align: middle; padding: 3px; cursor: pointer; display: inline; position: static !important;\" width=\"631\" height=\"210\"></p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">我也没有去深入研究，只好通过下面手工加载工具包镜像的方式来安装了。</p><h3 id=\"articleHeader1\" class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: inherit; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; font-size: 1.5em;\">手工加载 VBoxGuestAdditions 光盘镜像</h3><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">在 virtualbox 包里面，有个&nbsp;<code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); padding: 2px 4px;\">VBoxGuestAdditions.iso</code>&nbsp;文件，本来上一步骤的 devices 菜单里面点击 insert 就是装载这个镜像，但是不知道为什么失败，所以，我就准备手工装载他。</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">首先，在&nbsp;<code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); padding: 2px 4px;\">Finder</code>&nbsp;-&nbsp;<code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); padding: 2px 4px;\">应用程序</code>&nbsp;中找到&nbsp;<code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); padding: 2px 4px;\">virtualbox</code>，右键点击，选择<code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); padding: 2px 4px;\">显示包内容</code>。进入&nbsp;<code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); padding: 2px 4px;\">Contents/MacOS/</code>，找到&nbsp;<code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); padding: 2px 4px;\">VBoxGuestAdditions.iso</code>，将其复制到桌面.</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\"><img id=\"<D98D5785-3C1C-4257-99E4-07E87C17D70C>\" src=\"quiver-image-url/E05A4BA8E3EF0DB6480FA23FBF52CE53.png\" alt=\"bVAjFn\" data-src=\"/img/bVAjFn\" apple-inline=\"yes\" apple-width=\"yes\" apple-height=\"yes\" class=\"Apple-web-attachment Singleton\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); vertical-align: middle; padding: 3px; cursor: pointer; display: inline; position: static !important;\" width=\"540\" height=\"342\"></p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">你也可以在终端下，通过下面命令拷贝到桌面。</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\"><img id=\"<D23A884D-48CD-4F29-B7EC-4C713DE78153>\" src=\"quiver-image-url/A20E9463AC558090B4E0D373CF9B9711.png\" alt=\"bVAjFx\" data-src=\"/img/bVAjFx\" apple-inline=\"yes\" apple-width=\"yes\" apple-height=\"yes\" class=\"Apple-web-attachment Singleton\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); vertical-align: middle; padding: 3px; cursor: pointer; display: inline; position: static !important;\" width=\"689\" height=\"101\"></p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">将这个镜像装载到 virtualbox 的虚拟光驱，如果你已经启动系统，可以通过如下方式装载。</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\"><img id=\"<8F727AA5-FBD2-4103-B071-03D45B8D9B66>\" src=\"quiver-image-url/9C72E41B599EBF98EAE873DCE2B42E89.png\" alt=\"bVAjGM\" data-src=\"/img/bVAjGM\" apple-inline=\"yes\" apple-width=\"yes\" apple-height=\"yes\" class=\"Apple-web-attachment Singleton\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); vertical-align: middle; padding: 3px; cursor: pointer; display: inline; position: static !important;\" width=\"514\" height=\"254\"></p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">也许你会出现下面的错误，点击 Details ，可以看到 mount 不成功。那就点击&nbsp;<code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); padding: 2px 4px;\">Force Unmount</code>&nbsp;忽视他咯。</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\"><img id=\"<A38AABB5-9AD5-4AE9-A438-13935B830550>\" src=\"quiver-image-url/CC2C61D5B47BD3EDC8D88E76027A5D8C.png\" alt=\"bVAjGO\" data-src=\"/img/bVAjGO\" apple-inline=\"yes\" apple-width=\"yes\" apple-height=\"yes\" class=\"Apple-web-attachment Singleton\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); vertical-align: middle; padding: 3px; cursor: pointer; display: inline; position: static !important;\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\"></p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">当然，我们还是要点击那个<img id=\"<108749FB-889F-4B8B-B527-2A9ADC148CA3>\" src=\"quiver-image-url/DA1B9148AF4E08B7E5A8992DF87C3CD9.png\" alt=\"bVAjHI\" data-src=\"/img/bVAjHI\" apple-inline=\"yes\" apple-width=\"yes\" apple-height=\"yes\" class=\"Apple-web-attachment Singleton\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); vertical-align: middle; padding: 3px; cursor: pointer; display: inline; position: static !important;\" width=\"23\" height=\"24\">光盘，确认已经把 iso 已经放入了虚拟驱动设备。</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">此时，<span class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">我想到为什么用 virtualbox 默认的菜单安装会出现失败了</span>，因为，在 virtualbox 的设置里，我们是将光驱放在 IDE 控制器下的，如下图</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\"><img id=\"<8E4A8387-7A38-410C-8710-644543EFD054>\" src=\"quiver-image-url/AB9DC5C80B4BD784324D28E2AF8C3BCF.png\" alt=\"bVAjKv\" data-src=\"/img/bVAjKv\" apple-inline=\"yes\" apple-width=\"yes\" apple-height=\"yes\" class=\"Apple-web-attachment Singleton\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); vertical-align: middle; padding: 3px; cursor: pointer; display: inline; position: static !important;\" width=\"795\" height=\"688\"></p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">IDE 设备在 linux 系统，默认应该是 hd 带头的设备，如 hda，hdb…… ，但 CentOS7 面向的大部分都是服务器设备，服务器一般不采用 IDE 控制器，而是采用更先进的 SCSI 作为硬盘等外设接口。因为是虚拟机，CentOS 就 IDE 设备也识别为 SCSI 设备了，所以，在系统里面显示为 sr0.我们可以用 lsscsi 命令查看，就可以看到我们连接的虚拟设备。</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\"><img id=\"<A99FB62C-BA60-4EB0-9B22-A3CF861FA255>\" alt=\"bVAjK4\" data-src=\"/img/bVAjK4\" apple-inline=\"yes\" apple-width=\"yes\" apple-height=\"yes\" class=\"Apple-web-attachment Singleton\" src=\"quiver-image-url/167C781A24CCDD0BEFA82E4168BD010A.png\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); vertical-align: middle; padding: 3px; cursor: pointer; display: inline; position: static !important;\" width=\"800\" height=\"138\"></p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">因为我们把光驱挂在 IDE 控制器下，则 virtualbox 默认的 mount 命令应该是&nbsp;<code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); padding: 2px 4px;\">mount /dev/hda /media/cdrom</code>&nbsp;这种类型的，结果找不到 hda 设备，mount 就失败了。下面，我们将 mount 命令修改如下（需要 root 权限）：</p><pre class=\"nginx hljs\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border: none; border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px; background-image: url(https://sf-static.b0.upaiyun.com/v-57aafee9/global/img/blueprint.png); background-size: 30px, 30px; max-height: 35em; position: relative;\"><code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 1em; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: inherit; background-image: none; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><span class=\"hljs-title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(133, 153, 0);\">mkdir</span> /media/cdrom\nmount /dev/sr0 /media/cdrom\n</code></pre><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">出现下面提示，表示 mount 成功。进入 /media/cdrom 目录，即可查看到相关文件。</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\"><img id=\"<AA47433E-CAAF-492F-B619-A896DC1ECD05>\" alt=\"bVAjLF\" data-src=\"/img/bVAjLF\" apple-inline=\"yes\" apple-width=\"yes\" apple-height=\"yes\" class=\"Apple-web-attachment Singleton\" src=\"quiver-image-url/465D14CE66948DAE369198A698A131AE.png\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); vertical-align: middle; padding: 3px; cursor: pointer; display: inline; position: static !important;\" width=\"633\" height=\"158\"></p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">执行下面命令，安装 VBoxGuestAdditions 增强包</p><pre class=\"hljs\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border: none; border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px; background-image: url(https://sf-static.b0.upaiyun.com/v-57aafee9/global/img/blueprint.png); background-size: 30px, 30px; max-height: 35em; position: relative;\"><code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 1em; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: inherit; background-image: none; overflow-wrap: normal;\">./VBoxLinuxAdditions.run\n</code></pre><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">运行成功后，截图如下：</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\"><img id=\"<77537EF1-23AC-4AD2-AF51-6B1AFDCD40AF>\" src=\"quiver-image-url/19E7BE758534A9F81FF2576AD69E5070.png\" alt=\"bVAjLM\" data-src=\"/img/bVAjLM\" apple-inline=\"yes\" apple-width=\"yes\" apple-height=\"yes\" class=\"Apple-web-attachment Singleton\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); vertical-align: middle; padding: 3px; cursor: pointer; display: inline; position: static !important;\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\"></p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">也许，你可能会出现运行不成功的情况，尤其如果你默认安装的是 CentOS 7 mini 版本。<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">那么执行&nbsp;<code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); padding: 2px 4px;\">./VBoxLinuxAdditions.run</code>&nbsp;之前，你需要先进行下面的操作。</p><h3 id=\"articleHeader2\" class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2; color: inherit; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; font-size: 1.5em;\">VBoxGuestAdditions 依赖包安装</h3><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">因为 VBoxGuestAdditions 编译会有很多包依赖，所以，需要先安装那些包依赖。</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">尤其是辅助包需要 linux 内核提供一些功能，这就需要内核的C header 来编译程序，也就是需要安装 linux-devel 这个工具。当然，kernel-devel 不光是 C Header 文件，它还有内核的配置文件，以及其他的开发用的资料。</p><blockquote class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10.5px 21px; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; font-size: 1em; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-color: rgb(0, 154, 97); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\"><div class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">if you have installed new setup of centos minimal or you haven’t installed yet, you need make, gcc, kernel-devel in order to Install VirtualBox Guest Additions installation script.</div></blockquote><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">On CentOS/Red Hat (RHEL) 6/5, EPEL repo is needed</p><pre class=\"ruby hljs\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border: none; border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px; background-image: url(https://sf-static.b0.upaiyun.com/v-57aafee9/global/img/blueprint.png); background-size: 30px, 30px; max-height: 35em; position: relative;\"><code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 1em; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: inherit; background-image: none; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(147, 161, 161);\">## CentOS 6 and Red Hat (RHEL) 6 ##</span>\nrpm -<span class=\"hljs-constant\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(181, 137, 0);\">Uvh</span> <span class=\"hljs-symbol\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(203, 75, 22);\">http:</span>/<span class=\"hljs-regexp\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(42, 161, 152);\">/<a href=\"http://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub\" class=\"\">dl.fedoraproject.org/pub</a></span><span class=\"hljs-regexp\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(42, 161, 152);\">/epel/</span><span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(42, 161, 152);\">6</span>/i386/epel-release-<span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(42, 161, 152);\">6</span>-<span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(42, 161, 152);\">8</span>.noarch.rpm\n \n<span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(147, 161, 161);\">## CentOS 5 and Red Hat (RHEL) 5 ##</span>\nrpm -<span class=\"hljs-constant\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(181, 137, 0);\">Uvh</span> <span class=\"hljs-symbol\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(203, 75, 22);\">http:</span>/<span class=\"hljs-regexp\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(42, 161, 152);\">/<a href=\"http://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub\" class=\"\">dl.fedoraproject.org/pub</a></span><span class=\"hljs-regexp\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(42, 161, 152);\">/epel/</span><span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(42, 161, 152);\">5</span>/i386/epel-release-<span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(42, 161, 152);\">5</span>-<span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(42, 161, 152);\">4</span>.noarch.rpm\n</code></pre><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">CentOS7 可以直接升级安装下列包</p><pre class=\"sql hljs\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border: none; border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px; background-image: url(https://sf-static.b0.upaiyun.com/v-57aafee9/global/img/blueprint.png); background-size: 30px, 30px; max-height: 35em; position: relative;\"><code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 1em; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: inherit; background-image: none; overflow-wrap: normal;\">yum <span class=\"hljs-operator\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(133, 153, 0);\">update</span>\nyum <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(133, 153, 0);\">install</span> gcc kernel-devel kernel-headers dkms make bzip2 \nreboot\n</span></code></pre><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">接下来就和上面的步骤一样，挂着 cdrom ，执行安装程序（run 安装命令需要 root 权限）:</p><pre class=\"bash hljs\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border: none; border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px; background-image: url(https://sf-static.b0.upaiyun.com/v-57aafee9/global/img/blueprint.png); background-size: 30px, 30px; max-height: 35em; position: relative;\"><code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 1em; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: inherit; background-image: none; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 139, 210);\">cd</span> media\nmkdir cdrom\nmount /dev/sr0 /media/cdrom\n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(38, 139, 210);\">cd</span> /media/cdrom\n./VBoxLinuxAdditions.run\n</code></pre><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">如果不想出现 xrog 警告提醒，可以添加参数<code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); padding: 2px 4px;\">--nox11</code></p><pre class=\"sql hljs\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border: none; border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px; background-image: url(https://sf-static.b0.upaiyun.com/v-57aafee9/global/img/blueprint.png); background-size: 30px, 30px; max-height: 35em; position: relative;\"><code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 1em; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: inherit; background-image: none; overflow-wrap: normal;\">./VBoxLinuxAdditions.run <span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(147, 161, 161);\">--nox11</span>\n</code></pre><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">如果还有其他错误，看命令执行后的报错信息. 如果你只想运行在 centos minimal 下, 因为没有图形组件，Xorg 是可以被接受的。😉</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px;\">接着，重启设备，增强包就安装成功了。</p><pre class=\"nginx hljs\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border: none; border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px; background-image: url(https://sf-static.b0.upaiyun.com/v-57aafee9/global/img/blueprint.png); background-size: 30px, 30px; max-height: 35em; position: relative;\"><code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 1em; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: inherit; background-image: none; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><span class=\"hljs-title\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(133, 153, 0);\">reboot</span>\n</code></pre><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px;\">如果你不满足于字符界面，那么请再移步<a href=\"https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000006233614\" class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 154, 97); text-decoration: none; outline: 0px;\">CentOS7 图形界面安装篇</a>。</p></div><div class=\"mt10 clearfix\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 10px !important;\"><ul class=\"article-operation list-inline pull-left\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10.5px; padding-left: 0px; list-style: none; margin-left: -5px; float: left !important;\"><li class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; padding-left: 5px; padding-right: 5px;\"><a href=\"https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000006233585\" class=\"text-muted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); text-decoration: none; outline: 0px;\">21 小时前发布</a></li>&nbsp;<li class=\"dropdown\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; display: inline-block; padding-left: 5px; padding-right: 5px;\"><a class=\"text-muted dropdown-toggle\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); outline: 0px;\">更多</a></li></ul></div>"
